Plate 1.0.0
!!! CURRENTLY WORK IN PROGRESS !!!
---
Plate is a simple program which parses CSV data from a file, into a template. Specifically, I built this for data-heavy, static website generation for pages with heavy reliance on iteratable data.

Plate uses CSV because its easy to implement. Included in this project is a json2csv converter script that uses jq.

I use this project for my personal website, where plate uses parsed GitHub API data to populate the page

# BUILD:
make

# INSTALL:
sudo make install
